$ON_HOUREGDAT
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_HOUREGDAT(zc) From W1CTR4
Return

Subprog AS_HOUREGDAT(VALEUR)
Variable Date    VALEUR
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
## Action STD
Call AS_HOUREGDAT(VALEUR) From SUBCTR
If mkstat=2
 [M]HOUREGDAT(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo HOUREGDAT(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
If !mkstat
 ## Action SUBCTRLEG
 Call BEFORE_ENTRY(VALEUR) From SUBCTRLEG
 If mkstat=2
  [M]HOUREGDAT(INDIC) = VALEUR
  Affzo HOUREGDAT(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
 Endif
Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

